  <recipe>
    <head>
      <title>Alabama Fizz</title>
      <categories>
        <cat>Beverages -</cat>
        <cat>Alcoholic</cat></categories>
      <yield>1</yield></head>
    <ingredients>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty/>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>Juice of 1/2 lemon</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>1</qty>
          <unit>teaspoon</unit></amt>
        <item>Powdered Sugar</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>2</qty>
          <unit>ounces</unit></amt>
        <item>Gin</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty/>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>Club Soda</item></ing></ingredients>
    <directions>
      <step>  Shake well with cracked ice and strain into highball glass over two ice
  cubes. Fill with club soda. Garnish with two sprigs of fresh mint.
  
  Recipe by: Mr. Boston
  
